<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 10:07:40 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列国家检察官支持调查利库德集团议员兜售加沙阴谋</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-01/ty-article/.premium/israels-state-prosecutor-supports-investigating-lawmaker-peddling-in-gaza-conspiracies/0000018d-637b-d2ef-ab8f-eb7b36d90000</link><description>利库德集团成员塔利·戈特利夫散布虚假阴谋论，并揭露抗议运动领袖希克马·布雷斯勒的丈夫为辛贝特安全部门工作</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 07:30:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-01/ty-article/.premium/israels-state-prosecutor-supports-investigating-lawmaker-peddling-in-gaza-conspiracies/0000018d-637b-d2ef-ab8f-eb7b36d90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列将患有阿尔茨海默氏症的 82 岁加沙妇女作为“非法战斗人员”关押两个月</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-held-gaza-woman-82-with-alzheimers-for-two-months-as-an-unlawful-combatant/0000018d-613a-de6e-a79f-73bbc94d0000</link><description>法哈米亚·卡里迪 (Fahamiya Khalidi) 因以色列国防军炮击而逃离家园，12 月初，以色列士兵在加沙的一所学校逮捕了她。她被转移到达蒙监狱，在那里她被拒绝与律师会面，直到上诉后才被释放</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 04:00:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-held-gaza-woman-82-with-alzheimers-for-two-months-as-an-unlawful-combatant/0000018d-613a-de6e-a79f-73bbc94d0000</guid></item><item><title>据报道，伊朗因担心以色列袭击而从叙利亚遣返高级官员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-01/ty-article-live/idf-commander-killed-in-gaza-fighting-hamas-inches-toward-accepting-hostage-deal/0000018d-62b7-d3da-af8f-62bfa1e40000</link><description>美国军方表示，袭击了也门的胡塞武装无人机基地和 10 架攻击无人机 ■ 布林肯会见联合国加沙协调员，讨论紧急人道主义援助 ■ 以色列国防军公布在加沙地带战斗中丧生的军官姓名 ■ 哈马斯消息人士称，哈马斯政治首脑将同意释放潜在人质如果协议能够保证延长停火 ■ 巴勒斯坦报道：拉法一名伊斯兰圣战成员被暗杀，四人死亡，其中包括一名儿童</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 03:41:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-01/ty-article-live/idf-commander-killed-in-gaza-fighting-hamas-inches-toward-accepting-hostage-deal/0000018d-62b7-d3da-af8f-62bfa1e40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列犯罪头目被单独监禁，引发对监狱长报复袭击的担忧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-crime-boss-placed-in-solitary-sparking-fear-of-revenge-attacks-on-wardens/0000018d-6139-d99b-abaf-e77f255e0000</link><description>当局在臭名昭著的犯罪组织头目奥德·库泰尔 (Odeh Kuthair) 的牢房中发现一部手机而受到惩罚后，里莫尼姆 (Rimonim) 监狱的看守被要求遮住脸</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 01:11:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-crime-boss-placed-in-solitary-sparking-fear-of-revenge-attacks-on-wardens/0000018d-6139-d99b-abaf-e77f255e0000</guid></item><item><title>由于胡塞武装袭击，数千只羔羊和小牛被困在运往以色列的船上，处境悲惨</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/thousands-of-livestock-stuck-on-ship-to-israel-in-dire-conditions-due-to-houthi-attacks/0000018d-60ab-d897-a3ef-e3bba9140000</link><description>由于目前红海的安全威胁，该船已两次改道，将启程为期一个月的航行。非政府组织以色列反对生鲜运输呼吁农业部“停止这种疯狂行为”</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 20:30:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/thousands-of-livestock-stuck-on-ship-to-israel-in-dire-conditions-due-to-houthi-attacks/0000018d-60ab-d897-a3ef-e3bba9140000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队占领加沙房屋，然后将其烧毁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-occupies-gaza-homes-then-burns-them-down/0000018d-6021-d16e-a39f-7f3f01e30000</link><description>《国土报》获得的信息显示，以色列国防军指挥官在未经法律批准的情况下命令士兵放火烧毁加沙废弃房屋。数百处已遭到不可挽回的损坏</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 20:06:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-occupies-gaza-homes-then-burns-them-down/0000018d-6021-d16e-a39f-7f3f01e30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列精锐部队军官在加沙地带战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/officer-in-elite-israeli-army-unit-killed-in-gaza-strip-combat/0000018d-60fa-d99b-abaf-e7fe11510000</link><description>来自以色列北部的 36 岁少校伊扎尔·霍夫曼 (Yizhar Hofman) 在周三的战斗中身亡。 10月7日，参加贝埃里基布兹战役</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 19:36:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/officer-in-elite-israeli-army-unit-killed-in-gaza-strip-combat/0000018d-60fa-d99b-abaf-e7fe11510000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔对美国犹太人和白宫的求爱达到高潮</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-31/ty-article/.highlight/qatars-courtship-of-u-s-jews-and-the-white-house-comes-to-a-climax/0000018d-607c-d897-a3ef-e3fd3f820000</link><description>美国犹太领导人和两党议员对卡塔尔未能充分利用其对哈马斯的影响力越来越不耐烦，他们的挫败感正以前所未有的方式显现出来</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 17:50:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-31/ty-article/.highlight/qatars-courtship-of-u-s-jews-and-the-white-house-comes-to-a-climax/0000018d-607c-d897-a3ef-e3fd3f820000</guid></item><item><title>以色列 LGBTQ 团体批评针对极端正统成员的“犹太手机法”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/israeli-lgbtq-groups-criticize-kosher-cell-phone-law-for-ultra-orthodox-members/0000018d-6023-d5e3-abfd-75fb04380000</link><description>议会委员会将听取一项新的“犹太手机法”提案，该法将阻止 LGBTQ 求助热线通过拉比认证的手机提供 24/7 服务，因此不被视为紧急服务</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 17:31:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/israeli-lgbtq-groups-criticize-kosher-cell-phone-law-for-ultra-orthodox-members/0000018d-6023-d5e3-abfd-75fb04380000</guid></item><item><title>“令人沮丧的是保持沉默”：以色列-巴勒斯坦和平组织回应 BDS 的说法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/disheartening-to-be-silenced-israeli-palestinian-peace-group-responds-to-bds-claims/0000018d-5fe0-d7f9-a3af-dfe86c950000</link><description>“站在一起”运动被 BDS 贴上“思想上不诚实”的标签，导致该组织发表声明强调“争取巴勒斯坦解放的斗争是多方面的”</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 15:12:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/disheartening-to-be-silenced-israeli-palestinian-peace-group-responds-to-bds-claims/0000018d-5fe0-d7f9-a3af-dfe86c950000</guid></item><item><title>为什么 BDS 不能容忍以色列的犹太人和巴勒斯坦人站在一起</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-31/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-bds-cant-tolerate-jews-and-palestinians-in-israel-standing-together/0000018d-5f07-d4f8-a9df-5f2f88ca0000</link><description>“站在一起”是以色列一项快速发展的草根运动，旨在将犹太人和阿拉伯人团结在一起。它对抗占领，它处于反对加沙战争抗议的最前线，它探视人质的家人。现在，一个重要的 BDS 组织正在呼吁抵制它</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 15:09:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-31/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-bds-cant-tolerate-jews-and-palestinians-in-israel-standing-together/0000018d-5f07-d4f8-a9df-5f2f88ca0000</guid></item><item><title>随着提名结束，加沙和乌克兰成为诺贝尔和平奖议程的首要议题；以色列组织提名</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/gaza-and-ukraine-on-top-of-nobel-peace-prize-agenda-israeli-orgs-nominated/0000018d-5f18-d4f8-a9df-5f3c7fba0000</link><description>由 10 月 7 日受害者维维安·西尔弗 (Vivian Silver) 共同创立的以色列组织 Women Wage Peace 是该奖项的提名之一。在大约 300 名提名中，许多人与加沙和乌克兰的战争有关，其中包括驻加沙记者莫塔兹·阿扎伊萨 (Motaz Azaiza)</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 14:46:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/gaza-and-ukraine-on-top-of-nobel-peace-prize-agenda-israeli-orgs-nominated/0000018d-5f18-d4f8-a9df-5f3c7fba0000</guid></item><item><title>“这个政府把我们带到了不好的地方”：以色列的抗议运动重新回到街头</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-01-31/ty-article-podcast/the-government-is-taking-us-bad-places-israels-protest-movements-are-back/0000018d-5b09-d6b0-adcd-7fbb8d6b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 14:33:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-01-31/ty-article-podcast/the-government-is-taking-us-bad-places-israels-protest-movements-are-back/0000018d-5b09-d6b0-adcd-7fbb8d6b0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么这位以色列艺术家不会参加她在南非举办的展览</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-artist-has-a-new-exhibition-in-south-africa-she-wont-be-attending/0000018d-5b13-d0fc-a9bd-5f5fe5b30000</link><description>以色列艺术家莫兰·克利格 (Moran Kliger) 原定飞往开普敦参加她的展览开幕式，但 10 月 7 日的袭击、加沙持续的战争以及海牙审判造成的以色列和南非之间的敌意让她感到出发不安全</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 13:46:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-artist-has-a-new-exhibition-in-south-africa-she-wont-be-attending/0000018d-5b13-d0fc-a9bd-5f5fe5b30000</guid></item><item><title>纸上的恐怖：在新展览中，以色列设计师努力应对 10 月 7 日</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/horror-on-paper-israeli-designers-made-captivating-posters-on-october-7/0000018d-5f13-d0af-a3af-7fbf4e210000</link><description>一个关于哈马斯袭击的展览将有 70 张海报印在 70 x 70 厘米的纸上，分为七个类别</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 13:22:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/horror-on-paper-israeli-designers-made-captivating-posters-on-october-7/0000018d-5f13-d0af-a3af-7fbf4e210000</guid></item><item><title>“我的教室用品是一块橡皮和一把 AK-47”：以色列顶级讽刺节目嘲笑近东救济工程处</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/my-classroom-supplies-are-an-eraser-and-an-ak-47-top-israeli-satire-show-mocks-unrwa/0000018d-5f39-d4f8-a9df-5f3dd12b0000</link><description>以色列最受欢迎的喜剧小品节目《Eretz Nehederet》在最近 10 月 7 日发生与哈马斯有关联的指控后嘲笑了近东救济工程处。其中还有一位虚构的联合国秘书长，他对近东救济工程处感到震惊，他说，“当然，我认为我们需要将他们的资金增加一倍”</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 12:26:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/my-classroom-supplies-are-an-eraser-and-an-ak-47-top-israeli-satire-show-mocks-unrwa/0000018d-5f39-d4f8-a9df-5f3dd12b0000</guid></item><item><title>她儿时的大屠杀梦想使这位以色列电影制片人一路登上了奥斯卡奖</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/film/2024-01-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-animator-hoping-to-become-the-first-israeli-woman-to-win-an-oscar/0000018d-5b7d-de55-a99d-ff7fcfc10000</link><description>塔尔·坎特 (Tal Kantor) 希望十月份访问好莱坞宣传她的动画短片《给猪的信》，但加沙战争改变了一切，包括人们对她获得奥斯卡提名的感人作品的反应，该作品讲述了大屠杀幸存者以及同情心和同情心的力量。共情</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 10:44:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/film/2024-01-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-animator-hoping-to-become-the-first-israeli-woman-to-win-an-oscar/0000018d-5b7d-de55-a99d-ff7fcfc10000</guid></item><item><title>挪威敦促维持近东救济工程处的资金，表示没有收到以色列关于指控的通报</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/norway-urges-maintaining-unrwa-funding-says-it-wasnt-briefed-by-israel-on-allegations/0000018d-5eef-d4f8-a9df-5fef0bbe0000</link><description>这个斯堪的纳维亚国家敦促近东救济工程处的其他捐助国“反思更广泛的后果”，因为有报道称其员工参与了哈马斯和伊斯兰圣战组织 10 月 7 日的袭击，因此削减了资金。挪威外交部长表示，近东救济工程处是加沙 150 万难民的重要生命线</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 10:26:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/norway-urges-maintaining-unrwa-funding-says-it-wasnt-briefed-by-israel-on-allegations/0000018d-5eef-d4f8-a9df-5fef0bbe0000</guid></item><item><title>唱片公司因反以色列言论而终止与罗杰·沃特斯的合同</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/record-company-cuts-contract-with-roger-waters-amid-history-of-anti-israel-statements/0000018d-5ecf-d0fc-a9bd-5edf3f6a0000</link><description>《综艺》杂志网站报道称，这家德国公司此举也是继平克·弗洛伊德乐队创始人过去针对以色列、美国以及支持俄罗斯总统普京的言论之后做出的。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 10:01:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/record-company-cuts-contract-with-roger-waters-amid-history-of-anti-israel-statements/0000018d-5ecf-d0fc-a9bd-5edf3f6a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队公布了周二在加沙地带战斗中丧生的三名预备役军人的名字</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/israeli-army-names-three-reservists-killed-in-gaza-strip-fighting-on-tuesday/0000018d-5e49-d0fc-a9bd-5e5d93a00000</link><description>军方还表示，周二有五名士兵在加沙的战斗中受重伤。他们正在接受治疗，并已通知家人</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 07:53:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/israeli-army-names-three-reservists-killed-in-gaza-strip-fighting-on-tuesday/0000018d-5e49-d0fc-a9bd-5e5d93a00000</guid></item></channel></rss>